platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Focus Noodles is not your ordinary focus timer. Once youve set a time and gathered all your digital ingredients, place your phone face down to start and let your dish cook. When you lift your phone at any point, steam escapeshalting the cooking process. (Nobody likes undercooked noodles, right?). Focus Noodles delightful details add fun to your productivity sessions, and with enough hard work and determination, you might even earn the title of noodle master!
